###############################################################
---------------------
PYRHARCKADE 1.0B OPEN
---------------------
###############################################################


First step : create your file from the liste of roms you can get on :

	http://pyrharckade.tuxme.net/roms/

Get the file and replace the ROM_CONFIG_FILES.csv in the / of PYRHARCKADE


-----------------------------------------------------------------

Second step : Use the verif_roms.sh :

cd PYRHARCKADE/BIN/
./verif_roms.sh

This script generate an ROM_CONFIG_FILES with the roms can work

copie the /tmp/MAME_OK.txt on PYRHARCKADE/ROM_CONFIG_FILES.csv

------------------------------------------------------------------

Last step : Use the get_media.sh

This script get the folowing media in the good path of the PYRHARCKADE FE:

	* roms
	* snap
	* video
	* wheel
	* doc 

------------------------------------------------------------------

To start PYRHARCKADE :

go to cd ${HOME}/PYRHARCKADE/
and use start.py

./start.py


------------------------------------------------------------------

Note for the pi version :

In the next version


------------------------------------------------------

V1.0B OPEN : 1st version for all 
